OL,5, Starbucks illegally fired six workers  
OL,6, in New York state in a pushback against
OL,7, unions, a US National Labor Relations  
OL,8, Board (NLRB) judge has ruled.          
OL,10,FThe judge says the firm committed      
OL,11,F"egregious and widespread" violations  
OL,12,Fof federal labour law at its stores in 
OL,13,Fcities of Buffalo and Rochester.       
